item.title: First Commit
item.description: I hope this thing is working, I have never done anything like this before but hey, what better way of showing the stuff you’re doing than a blog on the internet that no one will probably find or read. Maybe it’s going to be a sort of therapeutical writing about what is happening in my projects so that I can organize my mind better, rubber ducky sort of thing. I have no expectations on this so at this point why not?
